ÚIn Loving Memory of
a great, fun & caring Husband & Father
Suky Hayre (1967 - 2014)
Love you always and forever until we are together again
Manjit & Calvin Hayre XXx

As a Coventrian Suky loved this park,
he trained here regularly with BMF
we often came running & walking here &
his beloved Coventry City Football Club
